pageTitle: WA State Licensing (DOL) Official Site: Vehicle scales in Washington State
textBeforeTable: If you can’t find a scale house near you on this list, please look in your telephone directory under “scales” or call your local vehicle licensing office for a recommendation. Below is a partial list of scale houses in Washington. These scale houses will charge a fee to weigh your vehicle and some will take payment in cash only. Before visiting a scale house, please call them to confirm hours of operation and ask about fees.
